Gifted Music Group’s new member, singer Allan Toniks has today dropped the audio & visusls for his long awaited song ‘Romance’ and it is his first song since he signing under the record label With production credit to Andre , “Romance” is faultless from start to end and the delivery by Allan Toniks will make you listen to it over and over. According to the singer, it is serious business this year since he has spent a lot of time in studio working on many songs that he is set to release this year including both singles and collabos with top East African artists Costumes, Location, Scripts & attitudes in this Video directed by J Blessing is nothing but superb, enjoy this adorable piece from the stable of Gifted Music Group. Note: There is a file embedded within this post, please visit this post to download the file. watch video below:  The post VIDEO: Allan Toniks – Romance appeared first on 360Nobs.com. Do you have something awesome to share with the world? Click here to share Do you ever have any question about anything you wish to ask and get answer? Click here to ask Follow us on twitter @NigeriaTodayNG Also, Like us on facebook This post was syndicated from 360Nobs.com. Click here to read the full text on the original website.